{"tid":1249330,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ESPN批評曼聯轉會操作遲鈍","createTime":"2019-06-21T16:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T06:16:23.000Z","uid":173952,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c7773071bb320d6612a0660022c7d5591dd75eba","tid":1249330,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"SPN批評曼聯轉會操作遲鈍，剛剛經歷了一個災難的賽季，中途換帥，無緣歐冠，和榜首差了32分，丟球數創造隊史英超之最。兩大死敵一個拿了國內三冠，一個拿了歐冠。重建最關鍵的夏天，距離新賽季備戰只剩10天，曼聯卻只花1500萬鎊買了個英冠的小妖。今夏的引援可能又悲劇了。​​​​"},{"pid":"1f6fe06a575813aa78364f08d9ae6e02a735acbe","tid":1249330,"uid":67225,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:15:38.000Z","msg":"都唔係第一日嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478bac060f264ed7c892c465598903896cc82075","tid":1249330,"uid":15644,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:17:07.000Z","msg":"叫阿木去買人<br />\n識條撚咩"},{"pid":"fba19fe03edd64bb2d799ebdf2a73435522a9017","tid":1249330,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"478bac060f264ed7c892c465598903896cc82075","tid":1249330,"uid":15644,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:17:07.000Z","msg":"叫阿木去買人<br />\n識條撚咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"阿木買人條件：<br />\n<br />\n英人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠social<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347d3ec13ce1d334cbc5bbcca4f4974dbaea4202","tid":1249330,"uid":15644,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:26:19.000Z","msg":"費sir 年代搵老將好撚準<br />\n白蘭斯 拿臣 奧雲  <br />\n唔一定有名氣<br />\n但係一定做到野<br />\n而家買埋神山果d 番黎 <br />\n竟然變左山狗<br />\n我都唔知係邊到出左問題"},{"pid":"b3ddd62ed6a6e45fd41205d1dece359dd6f814d9","tid":1249330,"uid":18520,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"347d3ec13ce1d334cbc5bbcca4f4974dbaea4202","tid":1249330,"uid":15644,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"20